---
title: Satay Pork Bowl & Asian Soy Veggies with Jasmine Rice & Roasted Peanuts
description: Pork and veggies over rice is a tried-and-true Asian-inspired favourite. But to get it just right, you have to hone in on the sauce,
which can make or break the dish. Luckily, we’ve got a good one: we’re blending creamy peanut butter with garlic, ginger and
soy sauce, then drizzling it all over to create waves of savoury flavour throughout.
